This is the most basic example of this library in use that takes advantage 
of the twitch wrapper that hides the threading of the library and also integrates nicer into unity. You can 

To connect to twitch chat you need a twitch user name, an oauth token and a channel to connect to. 
The Canvas in the scene has the wrapper along with an account field and a button that opens a browser
to a page where an oauth token can be retrieved.